=Kizil=
==Literature==
===Monographs===
===Articles===
* Angela F. Howard: In Support of a New Chronology for the Kizil Mural Paintings. Archives of Asian Art 44 (1991): 68-83
* Rajeshwari Ghose: "Buddhism in Kizil: Texts and Painted Imagery". In: The Art of Central Asia and the Indian Subcontinent. Edited by Anupa Pande. New Dehli: National Museum Institute, 2009: 123-133
* Marianne Yaldiz: "Maitreya in Kizil - Iconography and Dating". In: The Art of Central Asia and the Indian Subcontinent. Edited by Anupa Pande. New Dehli: National Museum Institute, 2009: 134-139
* 魏正中:《克孜尔谷西的石窟寺院》，《燕京学报》新十六期，2004年。
* 魏正中:《克孜尔石窟前的木构建筑》，《文物》，2004年，第10期
* Giuseppe Vignato: "The Wooden Architecture of the Kizil Caves" Journal of Inner Asian Art and Archaeology, 1 (2006): 11-27
* Giuseppe Vignato: "Archaeological Survey of Kizil – its Groups of Caves, Districts, Chronology and Buddhist  Schools", East and West, 56, 4 (2006): 1-58
* Giuseppe Vignato: "Towards a more reliable chronology for the site of Kizil: a discussion on method"  MARG，(2008): 32-39.